Step1: Run the following Command

```
npm install -D tailwindcss
npx tailwindcss init

```

Step2: Copy the following and paste it into the input.css file which you have created in the src folder

```
@tailwind base;
@tailwind components;
@tailwind utilities;

```

Step3: Initialize the content in the tailwindcss.config.js

```
content: ["./src/**/*.{html,js}"]

```

Step4: Run the following Command

```
npx tailwindcss -i ./Src/input.css -o ./dist/output.css --watch

```

Step5: Copy and Paste the following code and link the css file to the html file

```
<!doctype html>
<html>
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <link href="./output.css" rel="stylesheet">
</head>
<body>
  <h1 class="text-3xl font-bold underline">
    Hello world!
  </h1>
</body>
</html>


```
